Package com.sicomsa.dmt.svc

Class DownloadService

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.svc.DownloadService
All Implemented Interfaces:
DMTService, InstantSource
public class DownloadService extends Object implements DMTService
Default implementation of DMTService to consume the WS.

When you create a DownloadService you assign a SvcMessageFactory that will be used as the context to instantiate the concrete services this service will use.

You can set to this class a DownloadRepository that will be used to save the CFDIs downloaded. If you do not set one a default LocalRepository will be used.

Since:
1.0
Version:
2024.11.10
Author:
Beto Lopez
